properties.headline: Tornado Watch issued February 6 at 4:58PM EST until February 6 at 8:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
TORNADO WATCH 29 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 8 PM EST THIS EVENING FOR
THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN FLORIDA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 10 COUNTIES

IN THE BIG BEND OF FLORIDA

DIXIE                 FRANKLIN              GADSDEN
JEFFERSON             LAFAYETTE             LEON
LIBERTY               MADISON               TAYLOR
WAKULLA

IN GEORGIA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 15 COUNTIES

IN SOUTH CENTRAL GEORGIA

BEN HILL              BERRIEN               BROOKS
COLQUITT              COOK                  IRWIN
LANIER                LOWNDES               THOMAS
TIFT                  TURNER                WORTH

IN SOUTHWEST GEORGIA

DECATUR               GRADY                 MITCHELL
